{"tid":940805,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【美國之音】如果你使用華為設備　就不要指望我們與你有所往來","createTime":"2018-12-14T08:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T10:51:15.000Z","uid":47714,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"25e4ad66b3e4ca1160e38fa0e61c315ef102a64f","tid":940805,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:21:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/huawei-us-taiwan-impact-20181213/4700288.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fhuawei-us-taiwan-impact-20181213%2F4700288.html&d=fPCWDw3FhU9n97cnZSL7WMKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=177d929a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/huawei-us-taiwan-impact-20181213/4700288.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2005136\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2005136&d=fPCWDw3FhU9n97cnZSL7WMKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=e9045454\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2005136</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.rti.org.tw/assets/thumbnails/2018/12/13/20181213000017M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rti.org.tw%2Fassets%2Fthumbnails%2F2018%2F12%2F13%2F20181213000017M.jpg&h=3de7d4f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n商會會長韓儒伯表。(圖：中央社)<br />\n<br />\n韓儒伯指出，美國政府對華為的基本立場就是，「從網路觀點來說，如果你使用華為設備，就不要指望我們與你有所往來，例如技術上的合作。如果在你的國家有華為網路設備，如果我們的東西必須通過你，我們就會退出。」<br />\n<br />\n韓儒伯舉英國的例子表示，美國基於國安風險也會希望盟友不要使用華為設備。他說，即便原來英國電信已經決定採購華為設備，也因為美國的壓力被迫全部取消，銀行卻必須吸收損失，台灣也會面臨同樣的壓力，如果要和美國合作，就不能使用華為產品，「如果你要和我們互動，就不能有這些東西在你的系統裡，否則我們不會和你交往。」<br />\n<br />\n至於民間對華為產品的使用是否有風險及如何管理？韓儒伯說，他不認為以政府力量來禁止是一個可行的辦法，但政府可以做的是教育和告知人民，華為產品不安全，使用上有風險，讓人民自己做決定。從國家的層次來說也一樣，美國要台灣知道，華為的設備有安全風險，一旦使用「將會為美台關係造成負面影響」，台灣必須自己做決定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/VOAChinese/status/1073387928875909120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVOAChinese%2Fstatus%2F1073387928875909120&d=fPCWDw3FhU9n97cnZSL7WMKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=b11a8287\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVOAChinese%2Fstatus%2F1073387928875909120&h=59c9916a\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/VOAChinese/status/1073387928875909120</a><br />\n<br />\n美台商業協會會長韓儒伯接受美國之音記者鐘辰芳採訪時表示，&ldquo;美國政府對華為的基本立場就是如果在你的國家有 #華為網絡設備 ，就不要指望我們與你有所往來，例如技術上的合作。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"9cf3ebc469ae51a0d580a5089bf40ef0989debd9","tid":940805,"uid":26329,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:26:33.000Z","msg":"香港rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d271b699c2a687ca21742828c8365f64503f6e","tid":940805,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:29:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31dbc74f56fcd280bad3a1f38a8461b587d0255c","tid":940805,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:30:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2be6ce19baa64efd07d912a10a67728c1afc11c7","tid":940805,"uid":1069,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"9cf3ebc469ae51a0d580a5089bf40ef0989debd9","tid":940805,"uid":26329,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:26:33.000Z","msg":"香港rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:31:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你覺得唔用華為，香港就唔會rip?"},{"pid":"1654cd540b6fad7547e5453b8d89d4faf2874536","tid":940805,"uid":15880,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:32:46.000Z","msg":"香港: 華為硬件,我全都要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"